      <!-- .archive-header --> 
      <article id="post-315" class="post-315 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-hot"> 
       <header class="entry-header"> 
        <h1 class="entry-title"> <a href="http://www.hefuxing.com/?p=315" rel="bookmark">Table ‘performance_schema.session_variables’ doesn’t exist</a> </h1> 
        <div class="comments-link"> 
         <a href="http://www.hefuxing.com/?p=315#respond"><span class="leave-reply">发表回复</span></a> 
        </div>
        <!-- .comments-link --> 
       </header>
       <!-- .entry-header --> 
       <div class="entry-content"> 
        <h4 id="运行mysql时提示table-performanceschemasessionvariables-doesnt-exist">运行mysql时，提示Table ‘performance_schema.session_variables’ doesn’t exist</h4> 
        <h4 id="解决的方法是">解决的方法是：</h4> 
        <h4>第一步：在管理员命令中输入：</h4> 
        <pre class="prettyprint"><code class="hljs lasso has-numbering">mysql_upgrade <span class="hljs-attribute">-u</span> root <span class="hljs-attribute">-p</span> <span class="hljs-subst">--</span>force</code></pre> 
        <h4>第二步：重新启动mysql的服务：</h4> 
        <pre class="prettyprint"><code class="hljs dos has-numbering"><span class="hljs-winutils">net</span> stop mysql
<span class="hljs-winutils">net</span> start mysql</code></pre> 
        <p>再次运行MySQL，就解决了。</p> 
        <p>注意，两步缺一不可。</p> 
       </div>
       <!-- .entry-content --> 
       <footer class="entry-meta">
         本条目发布于
